The variety in the set, including turner tongs, spatula, spoon, brush, and whisk, covers all my kitchen needs. The fact that they are safe for nonstick cookware and dishwasher-friendly is a major plus. Not only are they functional, but the vibrant design also adds a pop of color to my kitchen. A fantastic investment for any home chef!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality for an affordable price
reviews.reviewText: Couldn't find all white cooking utensils that would match my white pots and pans. The ones I found come with either wood or silver handles so I decided to buy the closest color (khaki).PROs:- Sturdy but will not damage/scratch ceramic or tefal surfaces- Love the khaki color It is unique and pleasant to look at.- Comes with different utensils for various cooking use.- Affordable. The cheapest silicone cooking utensil I've found was priced $3.99 for a piece.- Includes a small container to hold the most frequently used ones.CONs:- Handle length may be short for taller people. The size is perfect for me but I'm 5'1."- The container is small and won't fit all the utensils.Overall a great product. It comes exactly as seen and as described on the pictures and desclription. Very affordable and definitely worth the money for the number of utensils you get.
